{"lemma":"حُورُ","slug":"حُورُ","root":"ح.#.ر","root_slug":"ح-_-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-_-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"حُورُ","root":"حور","pos":"N","occurrence_count":4},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n9451","n9452","n9453"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8F%D9%88%D8%B1%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be or become white"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/iħ.war.ra/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n9451","headword_ar":"حَوْرٌ","root":"Hwr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAra","text_ar":"حَارَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, A, Msb, K.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naEuw*u biA@ll~`hi mina AlHawori baEoda Alkawoni","text_ar":"نَعُوذُ بِا@للّٰهِ مِنَ الحَوْرِ بَعْدَ الكَوْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA on the authority of 'Ásim, and so in a copy of the S,) a trad., (TA,) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We have recourse to God for preservation from decrease,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"defectiveness, after increase,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"redundance:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mina AlHawori baEoda","text_ar":"مِنَ الحَوْرِ بَعْدَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alkawori","text_ar":"الكَوْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA, and so in copies of the S,) meaning as above: (S, TA:) or (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from a bad state of affairs after a good state;"},{"kind":"text","text":"from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaworN","text_ar":"حَوْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying the “ untwisting ” a turban: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from returning and departing from the community"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the faithful"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after having been therein;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAra","text_ar":"حَارَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"“ he untwisted ” his turban, and] from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAra","text_ar":"كَارَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"“ he twisted ” his turban upon his head. (Zj, TA. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaworN","text_ar":"كَوْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY maHaArapK","text_ar":"فِى مَحَارَةٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuwrN","text_ar":"حُورٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaworN","text_ar":"حَوْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Deficiency upon deficiency,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"return upon return,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) is a prov., applied to him whose good fortune is retiring; (S, K;) or to him who is not in a good state; or to him who has been in a good state and has become in a bad state: (K:) or the saying is, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN HaworN fiY maHaArapK","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ حَوْرٌ فِى مَحَارَةٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is suffering deficiency upon deficiency:"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaworN","text_ar":"حَوْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being used in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAy^irN","text_ar":"حَايِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baworN","text_ar":"بَوْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAy^irN","text_ar":"بَايِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: so heard by IAar; and said by him to be applied in"},{"kind":"page_break","n":666},{"kind":"text","text":"the case of a thing not in a good state; or to him who has been in a good state and has become in a bad state. (TA.) One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlbaATilu fiY","text_ar":"البَاطِلُ فِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaworK","text_ar":"حَوْرٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What is false,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vain, is waning and retreating."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wabuwrK","text_ar":"وَبُورٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahu fiY HuwrK","text_ar":"اـِنَّهُ فِى حُورٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuwrK buwrK","text_ar":"حُورٍ بُورٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hyr","text_ar":"حير"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily he is engaged in that which is not a skilful nor a good work"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"performance"},{"kind":"text","text":": ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY gayori SanoEapK walaA A_ijaAdapK","text_ar":"فِى غَيْرِ صَنْعَةٍ وَلَا اـِجَادَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":": so in the L: in the K, for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHAdp","text_ar":"احادة"},{"kind":"text","text":"is put"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_itaAwapK","text_ar":"اـِتَاوَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which is evidently a mistake]: TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he is in a bad state, and a state of perdition"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hyr","text_ar":"حير"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in error."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buwrN","text_ar":"بُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAy^irN","text_ar":"بَايِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bwr","text_ar":"بور"},{"kind":"text","text":"; where it is implied that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bwr","text_ar":"بور"},{"kind":"text","text":"is here an imitative sequent of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hwr","text_ar":"حور"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ahaba fulaAnN fiY","text_ar":"ذَهَبَ فُلَانٌ فِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAlbawaAru","text_ar":"وَالبَوَارُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHawaAri","text_ar":"الحَوَارِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one went away in a defective and bad state."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, TA.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HawiyrN","text_ar":"حَوِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What is beneath the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaworN","text_ar":"كَوْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a turban. (K.)       -A3-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bottom"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a well or the like. (K.) ―         -b2-  Hence, (TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa baEiydu AlHawori","text_ar":"هُوَ بَعِيدُ الحَوْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is intelligent;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deep in penetration."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","S","K"]},{"entry_id":"n9452","headword_ar":"حُورٌ","root":"Hwr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaworN","text_ar":"حَوْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places.       -A2-  Also [app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A return of flour for the loan of a hand-mill;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuqobapN","text_ar":"عُقْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoqaba","text_ar":"اَعْقَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":") signifying some broth which is returned with a borrowed cooking-pot:] a subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHArt","text_ar":"احارت"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TaHanato famaA","text_ar":"طَحَنَتْ فَمَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHaArato $ayoy^FA","text_ar":"اَحَارَتْ شَيْيًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v. suprà]. (S, K.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n9453","headword_ar":"حَوَرٌ","root":"Hwr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Intense whiteness of the white of the eye and intense blackness of the black thereof,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with intense whiteness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fairness, of the rest of the person:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intense whiteness of the white of the eye and intense blackness of the black thereof, with roundness of the black, and thinness of the eyelids, and whiteness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fairness, of the parts around them:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blackness of the whole"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of what appears"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the eye, as in the eyes of gazelles"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, S, Msb, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and of bulls and cows:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, S:) and this is not found in human beings, but is attributed to them by way of comparison: (AA, S, Msb, K:) As says, I know not what is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHawaru","text_ar":"الحَوَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the eye. (S.) ―         -b2-  Also [simply]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Whiteness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Red skins, with which"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"baskets of the kind called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"silaAl","text_ar":"سِلَال"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"are covered:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) [a coll. gen. n.:] n. un. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuwraAnN","text_ar":"حُورَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K, TA: in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HawarAnN","text_ar":"حَوَرانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or (so in the TA, but in the K “ and ”)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a hide dyed red:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"red skins, not"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as are termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraZiy~ap","text_ar":"قَرَظِيَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":": pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHowaArN","text_ar":"اَحْوَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (AHn:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skins tanned without"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaraZ","text_ar":"قَرَظ"},{"kind":"text","text":": or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thin white skins, of which"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"receptacles of the kind called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asofaAT","text_ar":"اَسْفَاط"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"are made"},{"kind":"text","text":": or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prepared sheep-skins."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [In the present day, pronounced"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hawor","text_ar":"حَوْر"},{"kind":"text","text":", applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sheep-skin leather."},{"kind":"text","text":"]       -A3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain kind of tree"},{"kind":"text","text":": the people of Syria apply the name of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaworN","text_ar":"حَوْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"to the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plane-tree"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dulob","text_ar":"دُلْب"},{"kind":"text","text":"); but it is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HawarN","text_ar":"حَوَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with two fet-hahs: in the account of simples in the Kánoon [of Ibn-Seenà], it is said to be"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain tree of which the gum is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"khrbA'","text_ar":"كهرباء"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh:) [by the modern Egyptians (pronounced"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hawor","text_ar":"حَوْر"},{"kind":"text","text":") applied to the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"white poplar"},{"kind":"text","text":":]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain kind of wood, called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlbayoDaA='u","text_ar":"البَيْضَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"because of its whiteness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHawaru","text_ar":"الحَوَرُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The third star,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[e,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that next the body, of the three in the tail of Ursa Major."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mir-át ez-Zemán, &c. [In the K it is incorrectly said to be the third star of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"banaAtu","text_ar":"بَنَاتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naEo$K AlS~ugoraY","text_ar":"نَعْشٍ الصُّغْرَى"},{"kind":"text","text":". See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqaAy^idu","text_ar":"القَايِدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qwd","text_ar":"قود"},{"kind":"text","text":".])"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","AA","TA","AHn","Mgh"]}]}}